  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8">お仕事のご依頼・ご相談はお気軽にどうぞ。</p>
    <a href="mailto:shiida.tetsuro@gmail.com"
       class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
        <path d="M2.003 5.884L10 9.882l7.997-3.998A2 2 0 0016 4H4a2 2 0 00-1.997 1.884z"/>
        <path d="M18 8.118l-8 4-8-4V14a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8.118z"/>
      </svg>
      shiida.tetsuro@gmail.com
